# pond is a local-first desktop app. Runtime secrets (ingest token, AI
# Gateway key) are stored in the macOS Keychain / Windows Credential
# Manager by the desktop app itself — there's no `.env` for the app at
# runtime. This file only exists for optional development tooling.

# AI Gateway key used by dev-only scripts that exercise the enrichment
# pipeline without running the full app. Leave unset in day-to-day dev.
# AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY="vck_..."

# Override the default port the extension talks to. Normally 41610.
# POND_INGEST_PORT="41610"
